To join Active Directory:

/opt/likewise/bin/domainjoin-cli join lab1.com administrator

To Link Vcenters on Host B:

cmsso-util domain-repoint --mode pre-check --src-emb-admin administrator --replication-partner-fqdn vcenter41.lab1.com --replication-partner-admin administrator --dest-domain-name vsphere.local

